title: Diamond Nights-Popsicle (Explicit Version) (2005)[MP3 192kbps]
description:
I discovered this band, and their album Popsicle last year and was immediately blown away.  The first song I heard was the first track of the album -- Destination Diamonds.

I finally just purchased this album, and I&#039;m so excited to share it.  

Popsicle was released in 2005, and I&#039;ve been actively tracking Diamond Nights on the net, but they don&#039;t seem to have any activity since a bout a year and a half ago. Does anyone know what happened to them? 

I would love to see this band live.
